== Your job ==
Break this feature into an ordered list of execution chunks ("ECs"). Each EC is a
coherent, independently buildable slice that will go through the FULL cycle
(design → review → code → test → deep-review) to completion before the next EC
starts. Order chunks so earlier ones unblock later ones (foundations first, then
features that depend on them, then integration/e2e).

Keep chunks meaningful — not too granular (avoid one chunk per file) and not too
broad (a chunk should be reviewable and testable on its own). 1 chunk is valid
for a small feature.

